{{Infobox film | name = Super Hero | image = superheromovie.jpg | caption = Super Hero Movie Poster | director = [[Ashiqur Rahman]] | producer = Taposhi Farooq | writer = Delwar Hossain Dil | screenplay = | story = | starring = {{ubl|[[Shakib Khan]]||[[Shabnom Bubly]]||[[Shampa Reza]]||[[Tariq Anam Khan]]||[[Tiger Robi]] }} | music = {{ubl|[[Akassh]]|Naved Parbez|[[Ali Akram Shuvo]]}} | cinematography = | editing = | studio = Heartbeat Production | distributor = Heartbeat Production | released = {{Film date|2018|07|16}} | runtime = 146 minutes | country = [[Bangladesh]] | language = Bengali | budget = | gross = }} '''''Super Hero''''' is a 2018 Bangladeshi action drama film. The film directed by [[Ashiqur Rahman]] and produced Taposhi Farooq.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bd-pratidin.com/entertainment/2018/06/14/337964 |script-title=bn:অবশেষে ঈদে আসছে শাকিব-বুবলীর সুপার হিরো |work=Bangladesh Pratidin |language=bn |access-date=2020-03-02}}</ref><ref name="ntvbd.com">{{cite news |url=https://www.ntvbd.com/entertainment/197195/সুপার-হিরো-ঈদে-আসবে-তো |script-title=bn:‘সুপার হিরো’ ঈদে আসবে তো? |work=NTV Online |language=bn |access-date=2019-03-18}}</ref> The film distributed by Heartbeat Production. It feature [[Shakib Khan]] and [[Shabnom Bubly]] in lead roles. Besides [[Tiger Robi]], [[Shampa Reza]] and [[Tariq Anam Khan]] and Others played an important role in the film.
The first look teaser of the film was released on May 27, 2018.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://thedhakatimes.com/100879/shakib-bublis-super-hero-teaser-published/ |script-title=bn:শাকিব-বুবলীর ‘সুপার হিরো’র টিজার প্রকাশ [ভিডিও] |work=The Dhaka Times |language=bn |access-date=2020-03-02}}</ref> It is the first Bangladeshi film filming in Australia.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.ntvbd.com/entertainment/177683/অস্ট্রেলিয়ায়-শুরু-হচ্ছে-শাকিব-বুবলীর-সুপার-হিরো |script-title=bn:অস্ট্রেলিয়ায় শুরু হচ্ছে শাকিব-বুবলীর ‘সুপার হিরো’ |work=NTV Online |language=bn |access-date=2019-03-18}}</ref>
== Cast == * [[Shakib Khan]] - Iqbal Mahmud Sami, a Special Force officer * [[Shabnom Bubly]] - Swapna Miliana Sima, Sami's love interest * [[Tiger Robi]] - Junaid * Salman Arif - Pitar * [[Sadek Bacchu]] - Kamal, Sami's father * [[Shampa Reza]] * [[Mahmudul Islam Mithu]] * [[Tariq Anam Khan]] - K.M. Khalil, a Bangladeshi missile specialist scientist * Cindy Rolling * Saiful Akbar Sadi
